OL,3,CChoosing a new pope: How the Vatican
OL,4,Cturns it's smoke signals black or white
OL,6,FCardinals are set to gather in Rome's
OL,7,FSistine Chapel on Wednesday to form a
OL,8,Fconclave and vote for the next pope.
OL,10,FFor centuries, Conclave, meaning "with
OL,11,Fkey" in Latin, has seen cardinals
OL,12,Flocked away until they agree on a new
OL,13,Fpope, ensuring the process is shrouded
OL,14,Fin secrecy and hidden from public view.
OL,16,FSo, how will people know when a new
OL,17,Fpope has been chosen?
