OL,3,CChoosing a new pope: How the Vatican
OL,4,Cturns it's smoke signals black or white
OL,6,FThe left stove is used to burn the
OL,7,Fballots, while the other stove creates
OL,8,Fthe smoke's colour.
OL,10,FWhat gives the smoke its distinctive
OL,11,Fblack or white colour?
OL,13,FTo create the different colours of
OL,14,Fsmoke, specific chemicals are added
OL,15,Fduring the burning process.
