OL,3,CChoosing a new pope: How the Vatican
OL,4,Cturns it's smoke signals black or white
OL,6,FShortly after a new pope is elected,
OL,7,Fhe steps onto the Vatican balcony,
OL,8,Fframed by red curtains, where he will
OL,9,Fdeliver his first apostolic blessing,
OL,10,Fknown as the "Urbi et Orbi" ("To the
OL,11,FCity and to the World"). This marks
OL,12,Fthe end of the conclave process.
